      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "AMALGAMATED FLYING SAUCER",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "CLUBS OF AMERICA, INC.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "IS - MISCELLANEOUS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "O FLYING SAUCER",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "The Philadelphia Division by letter dated 9/22/66, furnished the Los Angeles Division with Issue No. 24 dated July, 1966, entitled \"FLYING SAUCERS INTERNATIONAL\", which is the official journal of the Amalgamated Flying Saucer Clubs of America, Inc. The Philadelphia Division received the magazine from Mr. [REDACTED] Philadelphia, Pennsylvania on 9/19/66. Mr. [REDACTED] stated he subscribed to the magazine because his son had exhibited an interest in flying saucers and outer space. He said that on pages 2 and 3 of Issue No. 24 was an article which he believed expounded the Communist Party (CP) line.",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "For the information of the Bureau, the International Headquarters of the Amalgamated Flying Saucer Clubs of America, Inc. is located at 2004 North Hoover Street, Los Angeles, California. The article, on pages 2 and 3, were allegedly written by Master KALEN-LI RETAN, Head of the plant KORENDOR, which was received on 5/4/66 by special directional short-wave radio by BOB RENAUD.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "The indices of the Los Angeles Division contain no information identifiable with RENAUD, and no investigation has ever been conducted on captioned organization.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "No further action is contemplated in this matter by the Los Angeles Office, UACB. REC-61-82399-41",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "The foregoing is furnished to the Bureau for information.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
